Rhiannon Drake https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhiannon_Drake 0 Rhiannon Sarah Margaret Drake (born 13 July 1989) is a British stage, musical theatre, screen actress and musician. She is best known for playing Sabrina in the original West End cast of Grim, and her role in the musical film And You Were Wonderful, On Stage.
